The compiled dist/ink.wasm binary embeds Google Ink together with its
transitive dependencies (including Abseil and protobuf), each distributed
under their respective licenses. The Embind bindings (wasm-src/bindings.cc),
the Bazel staging in wasm-src/, the build scripts (setup.js, build.js), and
